		<content type="html" xml:base="/index.php/webdev/serverprogramming/automated-monitoring-of-remote-vnc-serve/#comment-3165"><![CDATA[<p>Yeah, interesting post and idea! I like the idea of maybe comparing the pixels to the desktop colour but I guess it depends on exactly what/how it has crashed as to whether that would work or not. And what happens if you get a BSOD&#8230;?</p>
